  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So after getting the invitation to the two bar mitzvahs, I said to my wife, [?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Lily, ?] let's go to Canada.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We've never been to Canada.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Let's go to Canada for the-- and [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Lily-- ?] and my wife said, Why should we go to Canada when we have a bar mitzvah right here in town?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I said, No, let's go to Canada.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We never been there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Let's go to Canada.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And by going to Canada, a change-- we-- we went to-- changed my life in an odd-- in a certain way.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The reason why, being at that bar mitzvah, sitting at the table and reminiscing with all the people at the same table about our war experience and questioning one another, what you did during the war and what the other person did through the war, I asked one person who was there where they spent the war.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they told me they spent the war in Russia.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the next question was, I said, did you heard about somebody from my home town?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my sister was married to a band leader.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He had a orchestra.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he had a quite famous orchestra.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I asked them, do you ever heard about the orchestra leader or about anybody in Russia?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He says, oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I think I heard about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In fact, the orchestra leader who's at this affair, he might tell you something about it because he spent time in the Russia too.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I went over to that orchestra leader, and I asked him if he knew something about.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, to bring it out, my sister and I separated during the war, just like I told you in the beginning of my story.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
